<!-- ── SERVICES ── -->
<section class="section" id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="tag">What We Do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Expert Azure Services,<br/>Delivered with Precision</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">We don't offer generic IT consultancy. Every engagement is led by a senior Azure architect with real-world delivery experience across enterprise and public sector.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">☁️</div>
        <h3>Azure Cloud Architecture</h3>
        <p>Design and deliver secure, scalable Azure environments aligned to your business goals. From greenfield builds to complex hybrid architectures — built right, from day one.</p>
        <ul style="font-size:14px; color:var(--grey-600); padding-left:18px; margin-bottom:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;">
          <li>Landing Zone design & deployment</li>
          <li>Hybrid & multi-cloud architecture</li>
          <li>Azure networking & security</li>
          <li>Cost optimisation & right-sizing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link">Discuss your architecture →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Cloud Migration & Transformation</h3>
        <p>Migrate confidently to Azure with a structured, low-risk approach. We manage the full journey — from assessment and planning to cutover and post-migration optimisation.</p>
        <ul style="font-size:14px; color:var(--grey-600); padding-left:18px; margin-bottom:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;">
          <li>Workload assessment & migration planning</li>
          <li>Lift-and-shift & replatforming</li>
          <li>On-premise to Azure migrations</li>
          <li>Risk management & rollback planning</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link">Plan your migration →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🏛️</div>
        <h3>Azure Governance &amp; CAF Alignment</h3>
        <p>Establish control across your Azure estate. We implement governance frameworks aligned to Microsoft's Cloud Adoption Framework, giving you visibility, compliance, and confidence.</p>
        <ul style="font-size:14px; color:var(--grey-600); padding-left:18px; margin-bottom:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;">
          <li>Management group & policy design</li>
          <li>RBAC, IAM & access governance</li>
          <li>Azure Policy & Blueprints</li>
          <li>Defender for Cloud & security posture</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link">Strengthen your governance →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h3>DevOps &amp; Infrastructure Automation</h3>
        <p>Accelerate delivery and eliminate manual toil with modern Infrastructure as Code and CI/CD pipelines. Build repeatable, auditable, and scalable cloud infrastructure.</p>
        <ul style="font-size:14px; color:var(--grey-600); padding-left:18px; margin-bottom:20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;">
          <li>Terraform & Bicep (IaC)</li>
          <li>Azure DevOps & GitHub Actions pipelines</li>
          <li>GitOps workflows & branching strategies</li>
          <li>Team coaching & capability uplift</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-link">Automate your infrastructure →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

