      <div>
        <div class="tag">Why IT Experts UK</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">A Different Kind of Azure Consultancy</h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
          Most consultancies assign whoever is available. We're different — you get direct access to a seasoned architect who has built and delivered Azure estates for some of the UK's most demanding organisations.
        </p>
        <div class="why-points">
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-point-num">1</div>
            <div class="why-point-text">
              <h4>No overhead, pure expertise</h4>
              <p>As an independent specialist, we offer enterprise-grade Azure capability without the large consultancy price tag or account management layers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-point-num">2</div>
            <div class="why-point-text">
              <h4>CAF-aligned, not ad hoc</h4>
              <p>All architecture follows Microsoft's Cloud Adoption Framework, ensuring your cloud platform is built on solid, scalable, and governable foundations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="why-point">
            <div class="why-point-num">3</div>
            <div class="why-point-text">
              <h4>We leave teams stronger</h4>
              <p>Knowledge transfer is built into every engagement. Your internal team will be better equipped long after we're done.</p>
            </div>
