<!-- ── OUR APPROACH ── -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <div class="tag">How We Work</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">A Structured Path to the Cloud</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every engagement follows a proven methodology — giving you clarity, control, and confidence at every stage.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="approach-grid">
      <div class="approach-step">
        <div class="approach-step__num">01</div>
        <h3>Discover &amp; Assess</h3>
        <p>We start by understanding your environment, goals, and constraints. No assumptions — just a thorough assessment of where you are and where you need to be.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-step">
        <div class="approach-step__num">02</div>
        <h3>Design &amp; Plan</h3>
        <p>We produce a clear architecture design and implementation roadmap, aligned to your priorities, timelines, and budget. You approve everything before work begins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-step">
        <div class="approach-step__num">03</div>
        <h3>Build &amp; Deliver</h3>
        <p>Hands-on delivery using Infrastructure as Code and automated pipelines. Clean, documented, repeatable — the way enterprise cloud should be built.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-step">
        <div class="approach-step__num">04</div>
        <h3>Enable &amp; Hand Over</h3>
        <p>We document everything and up-skill your team so they can operate confidently. You own the outcome — not just the subscription.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

