<!-- ── CASE STUDIES ── -->
<section class="section" id="case-studies">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="tag">Case Studies</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Real Projects. Real Results.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">A selection of recent engagements, showing the breadth of challenges we've solved for UK organisations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="case-grid">

      <div class="case-card">
        <div class="case-card__header">
          <div class="case-card__sector">Housing Association · Northwest England</div>
          <div class="case-card__title">Magenta Living — VMware to Azure Cloud Transformation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__body">
          <div class="case-card__challenge">The Challenge</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">Magenta Living, a not-for-profit housing association, needed to move away from a traditional on-premises VMware and SAN-based environment to a modern, cloud-first Azure architecture — whilst building internal capability to manage the platform long-term.</p>
          <div class="case-card__challenge" style="margin-top:16px;">What We Delivered</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">Led the end-to-end migration, delivering CAF workshops to align stakeholders, deploying Azure Landing Zones and NVAs using Terraform IaC, and standardising networking and security across all sites. Structured knowledge transfer ensured the internal team could independently operate and develop the platform after handover.</p>
          <div class="case-card__outcomes">
            <span class="outcome-tag">CAF Workshops</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Azure Landing Zone (Terraform)</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Lift-shift &amp; Re-architecture</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">NVA Deployment</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Team Enablement</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card">
        <div class="case-card__header">
          <div class="case-card__sector">National Charity · UK-Wide</div>
          <div class="case-card__title">The Woodland Trust — Cloud Migration &amp; Modernisation Programme</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__body">
          <div class="case-card__challenge">The Challenge</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">The Woodland Trust required a large-scale cloud migration and modernisation programme, including new Azure infrastructure, separate UAT and Production environments, and the modernisation of legacy data platforms — all while supporting parallel business transformation initiatives.</p>
          <div class="case-card__challenge" style="margin-top:16px;">What We Delivered</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">Designed and deployed Azure infrastructure to support migration and modernisation. Modernised data platforms from SQL IaaS to Azure SQL Managed Instance and Azure SQL Database. Led the organisation-wide Windows 11 rollout to ~700 endpoints via Microsoft Intune and Autopilot. Migrated the Azure DevOps organisation to a new tenant with improved security and governance.</p>
          <div class="case-card__outcomes">
            <span class="outcome-tag">Azure SQL Managed Instance</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">700-Endpoint Win11 Rollout</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Intune &amp; Autopilot</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Azure DevOps Migration</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Security &amp; Governance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="case-card">
        <div class="case-card__header">
          <div class="case-card__sector">Housing Association · Merseyside</div>
          <div class="case-card__title">South Liverpool Homes — Enterprise Landing Zone &amp; AVD</div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card__body">
          <div class="case-card__challenge">The Challenge</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">Contracted via Altair Ltd, South Liverpool Homes needed their Azure environment re-architected in alignment with Microsoft's Cloud Adoption Framework, with a focus on enterprise-scale Landing Zone design and automated infrastructure deployment.</p>
          <div class="case-card__challenge" style="margin-top:16px;">What We Delivered</div>
          <p class="case-card__text">Delivered a full CAF workshop and gap analysis, then designed and deployed a new Azure Landing Zone using subscription democratisation. Migrated a legacy VPN gateway to a zone-redundant Azure VPN gateway. Implemented Azure DevOps with Terraform CI/CD pipelines, and delivered two separate Azure Virtual Desktop environments — one for internal users, one for a sister housing association.</p>
          <div class="case-card__outcomes">
            <span class="outcome-tag">CAF Landing Zone</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Terraform CI/CD Pipelines</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Zone-Redundant VPN Gateway</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">Azure Virtual Desktop (x2)</span>
            <span class="outcome-tag">DR Roadmap</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

